                            <comment id="12697653" author="bryanduxbury" created="Thu, 9 Apr 2009 21:24:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We just decided to revert &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-236&quot; title=&quot;Structs should be serialized in a consistent order&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;THRIFT-236&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;THRIFT-236&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; instead. I&apos;ll reopen that issue so we can figure out how to have the right functionality there.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
